- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is also likely as the paper considers communication models between the robots. 
- cs.DS (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is relevant as the evacuation problem involves distributed robots. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes algorithms to solve the evacuation problem. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with controlling the movement of robots to evacuate a given area.
